title: Martin Taylor Guitar Retreat - New York 2016
description:
Information on the Martin Taylor Guitar Retreat in New York in 2016.

To register go to http://www.martintaylorguitarretreats.com

An amazing 4 days and 4 nights of learning, playing, eating and sleeping guitar in the beautiful Catskills Mountains. Just 2.5 hours from New York City this retreat will be limited to only 30 participants who will join Martin and his guest instructors for an unforgettable musical experience.
